      </p>
      
      <div class="term-point">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shop fa-icon"></i>
        <p>Buyers can purchase books from both bookstores and individual booksellers through the platform. This provides access to a diverse catalog ranging from the newest releases offered by established bookstores to rare and pre-loved titles from individual booksellers. Our integrated search and filtering system allows buyers to quickly find specific titles, authors, genres, or editions across all seller types. Personal recommendations based on purchase history and preferences are also provided to enhance the discovery experience.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="term-point">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-gavel fa-icon"></i>
        <p>Buyers may participate in auctions for books listed by booksellers and place bids according to the auction rules. When placing a bid, buyers enter into a commitment to purchase the item if they are the highest bidder when the auction closes. Automatic bidding is available, allowing buyers to set a maximum amount they're willing to pay, with the system incrementally increasing their bid as needed to maintain the leading position. Buyers will receive notifications when they are outbid or when auctions they're participating in are nearing completion.</p>
      </div>
      
